    <h1>Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)</h1>
    <p class="description">An AI framework that searches external documents before generating answers — powering Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT browsing, and Perplexity. Understanding RAG is how <strong>content gets cited by AI</strong>, not just ranked by Google.</p>
